		취미 :
		<input type="checkbox" name="hobby" value="요리">요리&nbsp;
		<input type="checkbox" name="hobby" value="축구">축구&nbsp;
		<input type="checkbox" name="hobby" value="게임">게임&nbsp;
		<input type="checkbox" name="hobby" value="영화">영화&nbsp;
		<input type="checkbox" name="hobby" value="농구">농구&nbsp;
		
		전공 : (name,value는 각각 정해주세요. 4개면됨)
		<input type="radio" name="major" value="정보통신">정통
		<input type="radio" name="major" value="간호">간호
		<input type="radio" name="major" value="경찰">경찰
		<input type="radio" name="major" value="태국어">태국어
		<input type="radio" name="major" value="일본어">일본어
		
